snippet.title: Ai to Yume no Kuni Sanrio Puroland - Chanto Dekiru Kana Minna to Tanoshii Oyuugikai (1998 Sega Pico)
snippet.description:
あいとゆめのくに サンリオピューロランド ちゃんと できるかな? みんなと たのしい おゆうぎかい is a Sega Pico game featuring characters created by Sanrio.

Please like this video and subscribe to my channel for more great retro content.
